data.name: Abstract
data.comment: A summary of the resource.

data.name: AccessRights
data.comment: Information about who access the resource or an indication of its security status.

data.name: AccrualMethod
data.comment: The method by which items are added to a collection.

data.name: AccrualPeriodicity
data.comment: The frequency with which items are added to a collection.

data.name: AccrualPolicy
data.comment: The policy governing the addition of items to a collection.

data.name: AlternativeTitle
data.comment: An alternative name for the resource.

data.name: Audience
data.comment: A class of agents for whom the resource is intended or useful.

data.name: AudienceEducationLevel
data.comment: A class of agents, defined in terms of progression through an educational or training context, for which the described resource is intended.

data.name: Bibliographic Citation
data.comment: A bibliographic reference for the resource.

data.name: ConformsTo
data.comment: An established standard to which the described resource conforms.

data.name: Contributor
data.comment: An entity responsible for making contributions to the resource.

data.name: Coverage
data.comment: The spatial or temporal topic of the resource, spatial applicability of the resource, or jurisdiction under which the resource is relevant.

data.name: Creator
data.comment: An entity responsible for making the resource.

data.name: Date
data.comment: A point or period of time associated with an event in the lifecycle of the resource.

data.name: DateAccepted
data.comment: Date of acceptance of the resource.

data.name: DateAvailable
data.comment: Date that the resource became or will become available.

data.name: DateCopyrighted
data.comment: Date of copyright of the resource.

data.name: DateCreated
data.comment: Date of creation of the resource.

data.name: DateIssued
data.comment: Date of formal issuance of the resource.

data.name: DateModified
data.comment: Date on which the resource was changed.

data.name: DateSubmitted
data.comment: Date of submission of the resource.

data.name: DateValid
data.comment: Date (often a range) of validity of a resource.

data.name: Description
data.comment: An account of the resource.

data.name: Extent
data.comment: The size or duration of the resource.

data.name: Format
data.comment: The file format, physical medium, or dimensions of the resource.

data.name: HasFormat
data.comment: A related resource that is substantially the same as the pre-existing described resource, but in another format.

data.name: HasPart
data.comment: A related resource that is included either physically or logically in the described resource.

data.name: HasVersion
data.comment: A related resource that is a version, edition, or adaptation of the described resource.

data.name: Identifier
data.comment: An unambiguous reference to the resource within a given context.

data.name: InstructionalMethod
data.comment: A process, used to engender knowledge, attitudes and skills, that the described resource is designed to support.

data.name: IsFormatOf
data.comment: A pre-existing related resource that is substantially the same as the described resource, but in another format.

data.name: IsPartOf
data.comment: A related resource in which the described resource is physically or logically included.

data.name: IsReferencedBy
data.comment: A related resource that references, cites, or otherwise points to the described resource.

data.name: IsReplacedBy
data.comment: A related resource that supplants, displaces, or supersedes the described resource.

data.name: IsRequiredBy
data.comment: A related resource that requires the described resource to support its function, delivery, or coherence.

data.name: IsVersionOf
data.comment: A related resource of which the described resource is a version, edition, or adaptation.

data.name: Language
data.comment: A language of the resource.

data.name: License
data.comment: A legal document giving official permission to do something with the resource.

data.name: Mediator
data.comment: An entity that mediates access to the resource.

data.name: Medium
data.comment: The material or physical carrier of the resource.

data.name: Provenance
data.comment: A statement of any changes in ownership and custody of the resource since its creation that are significant for its authenticity, integrity, and interpretation.

data.name: Publisher
data.comment: An entity responsible for making the resource available.

data.name: References
data.comment: A related resource that is referenced, cited, or otherwise pointed to by the described resource.

data.name: Relation
data.comment: A related resource.

data.name: Replaces
data.comment: A related resource that is supplanted, displaced, or superseded by the described resource.

data.name: Requires
data.comment: A related resource that is required by the described resource to support its function, delivery, or coherence.

data.name: Rights
data.comment: Information about rights held in and over the resource.

data.name: RightsHolder
data.comment: A person or organization owning or managing rights over the resource.

data.name: Source
data.comment: A related resource from which the described resource is derived.

data.name: SpatialCoverage
data.comment: Spatial characteristics of the resource.

data.name: Subject
data.comment: A topic of the resource.

data.name: TableOfContents
data.comment: A list of subunits of the resource.

data.name: TemporalCoverage
data.comment: Temporal characteristics of the resource.

data.name: Title
data.comment: A name given to the resource.

data.name: Type
data.comment: The nature or genre of the resource.
